---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Story | Sidharth Mohanty"
  description="Welcome to my page - Sid : )"
>
  <section class="story-hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-quote-container">
        <div class="quote-mark">"</div>
        <blockquote class="hero-quote">
          Through uncharted realms, I roam with might,<br />
          seeking treasures hidden out of sight.
        </blockquote>
        <div class="quote-mark closing">"</div>
      </div>

      <h1 class="hero-title">
        The Story Behind<br />
        <span class="title-accent">The Code</span>
      </h1>

      <div class="hero-subtitle-container">
        <div class="subtitle-line"></div>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">Code â€¢ Gym â€¢ Caffeine â€¢ Repeat</p>
        <div class="subtitle-line"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="story-content">
    <div class="content-grid">
      <div class="story-introduction">
        <div class="intro-header">
          <h2 class="intro-title">About Sidharth</h2>
          <div class="intro-line"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="intro-text">
          <p class="greeting">Hi there, I'm Sidharth ðŸ‘‹</p>

          <p class="intro-paragraph">
            I'm a Software Engineer II at Builder.io, where I'm currently
            working on world-class software that empowers developers globally.
            I'm a fullstack developer with over 3 years of experience crafting
            applications that solve real problems.
          </p>

          <p class="intro-paragraph emphasis">
            Web apps, mobile apps, chrome extensions, APIsâ€”I've explored them
            all. But here's the thing: <span class="highlight"
              >I'm still learning every single day.</span
            >
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="story-details">
        <div class="detail-section">
          <h3 class="detail-title">Technical Journey</h3>
          <div class="detail-content">
            <p>
              I've been a JavaScript enthusiast since day one. React, Vue,
              Angular, Node, Express, Nest, Next, Nuxtâ€”I've danced with them
              all. But that's not where it ends.
            </p>
            <p>
              I've ventured into the worlds of Golang and Python, creating APIs
              and CLI tools that bridge the gap between complex problems and
              elegant solutions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="detail-section">
          <h3 class="detail-title">Always Exploring</h3>
          <div class="detail-content">
            <p>
              When it comes to technology, I'm always hunting for the latest
              innovations. Backend architecture, DevOps practices, database
              optimization, system design, CI/CD pipelinesâ€”curiosity drives my
              exploration.
            </p>
            <p>
              The tech landscape is vast and ever-changing, and I embrace that
              complexity with enthusiasm and systematic learning.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="detail-section">
          <h3 class="detail-title">Beyond the Screen</h3>
          <div class="detail-content">
            <p>
              But I'm not all about the code. I'm a fitness enthusiast who
              believes in strengthening both mind and body. The gym is where I
              find balance, building physical resilience alongside mental
              agility.
            </p>
            <p>
              And coffee? It's the fuel that powers late-night coding sessions
              and early morning problem-solving marathons. Some call it
              addiction; I call it dedication.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="philosophy-section">
      <div class="philosophy-header">
        <div class="philosophy-line"></div>
        <h2 class="philosophy-title">My Philosophy</h2>
        <div class="philosophy-line"></div>
      </div>

      <blockquote class="philosophy-quote">
        "Knowledge is power, and I'm here to absorb it all. An eternal learner,
        always tinkering, experimenting, and solving problems. The tech world is
        my infinite universe, and I'm on an endless quest for discovering new
        horizons."
      </blockquote>
    </div>

    <div class="journey-timeline">
      <h2 class="timeline-title">The Journey So Far</h2>
      <div class="timeline-grid">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-number">01</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Student & Explorer</h3>
            <p>Computer Science at OUTR, Bhubaneswar</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-number">02</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Developer & Builder</h3>
            <p>2+ years crafting fullstack applications</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-number">03</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Open Source Contributor</h3>
            <p>Contributing to meaningful projects worldwide</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-number">04</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Continuous Learner</h3>
            <p>Always exploring new technologies and methodologies</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .story-hero {
    padding: 4rem 0 6rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    position: relative;
  }

  body.classic-theme.dark-mode .story-hero {
    border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) !important;
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hero-quote-container {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .quote-mark {
    font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #000000;
    line-height: 1;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .classic-theme.dark-mode .quote-mark {
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .quote-mark.closing {
    align-self: flex-end;
  }

  .hero-quote {
    font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #333333;
    margin: 0;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 500px;
  }

  .classic-theme.dark-mode .hero-quote {
    color: #dddddd;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: #000000;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 4.5rem;
    }
  }

  .classic-theme.dark-mode .hero-title {
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .title-accent {
    color: #666666;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .classic-theme.dark-mode .title-accent {
    color: #cccccc;
  }

  .hero-subtitle-container {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .subtitle-line {
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: #000000;
    max-width: 100px;
  }

  .classic-theme.dark-mode .subtitle-line {
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #666666;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    white-space: nowrap;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .classic-theme.dark-mode .hero-subtitle {
    color: #cccccc;
  }

  .story-content {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
      gap: 6rem;
    }
  }

  .intro-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .intro-title {
    font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #000000;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .classic-theme.dark-mode .intro-title {
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .intro-line {
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: #000000;
  }

  .classic-theme.dark-mode .intro-line {
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  .intro-text {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .greeting {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .classic-theme.dark-mode .greeting {
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .intro-paragraph {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #333333;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .classic-theme.dark-mode .intro-paragraph {
    color: #dddddd;
  }

  .intro-paragraph.emphasis {
    font-style: italic;
    border-left: 3px solid #000000;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .classic-theme.dark-mode .intro-paragraph.emphasis {
    border-left-color: #ffffff;
  }

  .highlight {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #000000;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .classic-theme.dark-mode .highlight {
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .detail-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .detail-title {
    font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #000000;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  body.classic-theme.dark-mode .detail-title {
    color: #ffffff !important;
    border-bottom-color: #ffffff !important;
  }

  .detail-content p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #333333;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .classic-theme.dark-mode .detail-content p {
    color: #dddddd;
  }

  .philosophy-section {
    margin: 6rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .philosophy-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .philosophy-title {
    font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #000000;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .classic-theme.dark-mode .philosophy-title {
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .philosophy-line {
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: #000000;
    max-width: 150px;
  }

  .classic-theme.dark-mode .philosophy-line {
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  .philosophy-quote {
    font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #000000;
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 700px;
    padding: 3rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    position: relative;
  }

  body.classic-theme.dark-mode .philosophy-quote {
    color: #ffffff !important;
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2) !important;
  }

  .philosophy-quote::before,
  .philosophy-quote::after {
    content: '"';
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #000000;
    position: absolute;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .classic-theme.dark-mode .philosophy-quote::before,
  .classic-theme.dark-mode .philosophy-quote::after {
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .philosophy-quote::before {
    top: 1rem;
    left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .philosophy-quote::after {
    bottom: 0.5rem;
    right: 1.5rem;
  }

  .journey-timeline {
    margin: 6rem 0;
  }

  .timeline-title {
    font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #000000;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .classic-theme.dark-mode .timeline-title {
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .timeline-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .timeline-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .timeline-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .timeline-item {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  body.classic-theme.dark-mode .timeline-item {
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2) !important;
  }

  .timeline-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .classic-theme.dark-mode .timeline-item:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .timeline-number {
    font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .classic-theme.dark-mode .timeline-number {
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .timeline-content h3 {
    font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .classic-theme.dark-mode .timeline-content h3 {
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .timeline-content p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #666666;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .classic-theme.dark-mode .timeline-content p {
    color: #cccccc;
  }
</style>
